How To Install Irssi Script
===========================
1. Put spotify.pl, spotify_playing.sh in ~/.irssi/scripts.
2. Run `/script load spotify.pl` in Irssi.
3. Try the script by running `/np` in Irssi.

C Version
---------
If you want a faster version, nun `make' and put spotify_playing in
~/.irssi/scripts.
